## Workflow

The Indel Visualizer pipeline automatically detects insertions and deletions (indels) from a pairwise sequence alignment in FASTA format and generates summary statistics together with publication-quality visualizations.

```text
                     Input
                        │
                        ▼
           Pairwise Alignment FASTA
                        │
                        ▼
             Load Reference & Query
                        │
                        ▼
             Validate Input Format
        (Exactly two aligned sequences)
                        │
                        ▼
         Scan Alignment Position-by-Position
                        │
        ┌───────────────┼───────────────┐
        │               │               │
        ▼               ▼               ▼
     Match         Mismatch       Gap Detection
                                        │
                          ┌─────────────┴─────────────┐
                          │                           │
                          ▼                           ▼
                    Insertion Detection       Deletion Detection
                          │                           │
                          └─────────────┬─────────────┘
                                        ▼
                         Calculate Alignment Statistics
                                        │
      ┌─────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┐
      │                                 │                                 │
      ▼                                 ▼                                 ▼
 Sequence Identity            Gap Percentage              Alignment Score
 Matches/Mismatches      Inserted & Deleted Bases        Gap Openings
                                        │
                                        ▼
                    Generate Summary Reports
      ┌─────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┐
      │                                 │                                 │
      ▼                                 ▼                                 ▼
alignment_summary.txt      alignment_statistics.csv      indel_summary.csv
                                        │
                                        ▼
                Extract Local Alignment Windows
                                        │
                                        ▼
        Generate Publication-Quality Figures
                                        │
                                        ▼
                        Output Directory
```

---

## Pipeline Steps

1. Read the aligned FASTA file.
2. Verify that the file contains exactly two aligned sequences (reference and query).
3. Compare both sequences position by position.
4. Detect matches, mismatches, insertions, and deletions.
5. Count:
   - Matches
   - Mismatches
   - Insertion events
   - Deletion events
   - Inserted bases
   - Deleted bases
   - Gap openings
6. Calculate:
   - Alignment length
   - Sequence identity (%)
   - Gap percentage (%)
   - Approximate alignment score
7. Generate summary reports in TXT and CSV formats.
8. Extract a configurable flanking region around each indel.
9. Produce publication-quality visualization for every insertion and deletion.
10. Save all reports and figures into the `Output/` directory.

---

## Input

```
alignment.fasta
```

The input FASTA file must contain **exactly two aligned sequences**:

```text
>Reference
ATCGATCGATCGATCG

>Read
ATCGAT--ATCGATCG
```

